Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 完全迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天到最后 樱小姐也没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱小姐到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然之前也有一直没回来的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全校学生罢课抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早天枷美夏的退学令正式发表了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理事会似乎想来个速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天校方决定对附中二年一班的天枷美夏作出退学处分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找替罪羊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教务办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要对理事会的决定提出抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广播后 所有对美夏退学处分定不满的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起拥到了教务办公室门口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果交涉破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍对教师的行为感到不满的学生们不愿回到教室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是这么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉锯战的罢课运动于是在校内升温
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直延续到现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我说 教导主任对学生会下达了镇压学生的命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会吗 那音姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然当场否决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大家都很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:04:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一班已经占领美术室 用雕塑作路障封锁中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打持久战了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以打响第一枪哦 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 那就好好帮他们打回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学 义之君也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱内 你在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在主角也出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是说曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你说啊 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是大家为美夏所做的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何一个人希望美夏离开学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家为美夏做这么多 我真的是非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这么做之后会有麻烦是大家不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管大家做什么 美夏的退学处分是不可能被取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是吗 杉並
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方只是受欲望支配的丑陋的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最多不过是给扣上不良分子的帽子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以美夏不希望为了这样无谓的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁了大家的大好前途
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么才能让大家停下来 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把你的想法告诉大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管用什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 大家一定会回应的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏的想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈佳 广播器材的使用方法你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？嗯 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杉並 广播室的钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 我就想到会有这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试音试音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…咳…今天运势很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 这也不用说吗 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见学园的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家安静地听我说 我是二年的天枷美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 是天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如大家所见 现在校园内发生了大动乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家为美夏所做的事 美夏真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但很遗憾 理事会的决定 美夏已经接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个决定不能收回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让天枷退学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}天枷天枷天枷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你去广播室的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的事继续下去 不但给周围的人造成困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会给大家自身带来麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏 美夏不希望大家为了美夏背上任何处分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏能转入大家所在的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起享受校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就剩最后三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家再让我渡过三天充实的校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 美夏就可以毫无遗憾地离开风见学园了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差几天了 就一点时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家给我一个享受平常校园生活的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 拜托了 拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一天 天枷的心意确确实实地传到了大家的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀哈 杏学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 来了啊 就等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把由梦也带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽井
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学这么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她现在这么开心 好像昨天什么也没发生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 这样下去真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之也是 对天枷同学的事好像也放手不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为天枷同学希望保持那种平常的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是小恋想做些什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然 因为是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但义之的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是因为讨厌那样才和义之君分手的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月岛小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽没错 真是的 奈奈佳坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 但如果真是这么想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就该小恋对自己诚实一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷把自己心里的想法告诉了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就轮到小恋站在朋友的立场去考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么去帮助天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有怎么面对义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看来其实就是这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见了 樱内 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈利马奥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来了 义之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 事前也没联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是理事会临时安排我出差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这只是理事会为了处分天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使出的调虎离山之计罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想像中的还轻松快活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经下了决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那义之呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之怎么看这事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么了结了真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 说实话我也在犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想为她做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷自己并不想让我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她比起自己 更关心我、由梦和班长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有风见学园的所有学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也想尊重天枷如此认真的考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让天枷就这样继续享受理所应当的最后一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像什么都没发生过一样继续过学校生活的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在这么想…很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 是不是对她太冷淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是非常好的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照义之所想的去做 这也都是为了天枷同学好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩下一点时间 就一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不出什么意外就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的愿望都连成一线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 约定好的三天期限转眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 结束了 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗 和美夏初次相遇时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想忘都忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那拳头我现在还痛着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 别提那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我也觉得抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后也一直给樱内添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 这么郑重地道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想道个谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着风见学园的学生身份还没失效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心我 我不是在感伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过 要是没有你 现在美夏还不知道怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在说些有的没的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏也通过认识你 第一次发现人类不全是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦和朝仓学姐 杏学姐 花咲同学 月岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带板桥和杉並 和大家都成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后也和泽井解开了心结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏真的是机器人与人类之间的桥梁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏的愿望实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 是义之吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了这么急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 天枷同学也在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那带上天枷同学一起来体育馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体育馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋这家伙 为什么要在体育馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业生入场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在校生起立
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你了 天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个是 天枷的毕业典礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏的毕业典礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 天枷同学 大家都等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么时候策划的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞成这样不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 学生会也全力协助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳乃校长也同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多亏小恋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这三天里月岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能让天枷同学毕业典礼可以成功举办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东奔西走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能为你做些什么真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我现在可以做到的全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,授予毕业证书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业证书 天枷美夏同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在任何时候都能保持健康明朗的心态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与同学相处融洽并完成了本学园所有规定课程
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特此证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见学园校长芳乃樱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:19:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}舞台的后台集合 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞台的后台？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 义之快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 好戏现在才登场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 饱含爽朗和激情叫出我们对美夏的爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:22:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
